(71, 'Vast Development Method', 'Joomla@vdm.io', 'Llewellyn van der Merwe', 'https://www.vdm.io/', '', 'Dynamically transition through different content panes.', 4, 'Switcher default', '', 5, 'http://getuikit.com/docs/switcher.html', 'The switcher component consists of a number of toggles and their related content items. Add the data-uk-switcher=\"{connect:\'#ID\'}\" attribute to the element which contains the toggles, targetting the same id as is used on the element containing the content items. Add the .uk-switcher class to the same element. Typically the switcher is combined with other components, some of which will be shown here.', '', 1, '2015-06-01 20:02:41', '2017-11-11 22:09:27', 10, '', 8, 'fd850fcf-366b-4b7e-9ccc-bb515f316ab7'),
(72, 'Vast Development Method', 'Joomla@vdm.io', 'Llewellyn van der Merwe', 'https://www.vdm.io/', 'In some cases you want to switch to another content section from within the active content. This is possible using the data-uk-switcher-item attribute. To target the items, you need to set the data attribute to the number of the respective content item.', 'Dynamically transition through different content panes.', 4, 'Switcher in-content', '', 5, 'http://getuikit.com/docs/switcher.html', 'The switcher component consists of a number of toggles and their related content items. Add the data-uk-switcher=\"{connect:\'#ID\'}\" attribute to the element which contains the toggles, targetting the same id as is used on the element containing the content items. Add the .uk-switcher class to the same element. Typically the switcher is combined with other components, some of which will be shown here.', '', 1, '2015-06-01 20:04:24', '2017-11-11 22:09:27', 10, '', 8, 'c2e83f1f-facd-43ba-ae8d-fc3ccc1debc7'),
